					<msContents n="1">
						<!--increment n attribute for ms containing multiple ms items-->
						<summary>There are charts. tables and diagrams on fol. 2A-B,3A,4A,6A-B,
							7A-B, 8A, 9A,10A-B, 11A-B, 12A,13B,14A-B; 17A-B, 22B, 24A-B, 25A, 29A,
							31A-B,34A, 35A, 37A, 38A-B, 39A, 40A-B, 41A-B, On fol.7B -a diagram of
							Mount Meru; on fol.14B - there is a kālacakra with descriptions of 6 ārās
							with it's 12 divisions.; On fol.17A - diagram of Lavaṇa samudra.; On
							fol.17B there are two diagramas at left - [TO CHECK DIAGRAM FROM DIARY TO
							COSMOLOGY WORK],; On fol.20A - a diagram of Vidyutaprabha ; On fol.20B -
							a diagram of Aḍhīdvīpa.; On fol.21A - a diagram of Vaitāḍhya mountain; On
							fol. 21B a diagram of Jaṃbū vṛkṣa.; On fol. 22A - a diagram of
							Jagatīcakra.; On fol.23B - a diagram of 14 Rājaloka.; on fol.26A - a
							diagram of Samaśreṇi.; On fol.34B - a diagram of four Kalasa.; On fol.35B
							- a diagram of Jaṃbūdvīpa measurement .;On fol.42A - a diagram of Rucaka
							parvatamāna</summary>
