							<note>Main Text</note>
							<!--<rubric xml:lang="pra" type="mula"><locus from="1v" to="1v">[1v1]</locus> 
</rubric>-->
							<incipit xml:lang="pra" type="mula"><locus from="1v" to="1v"
									>[1v1]</locus> Vīraṃ jaya-sehara-paya paiṭṭhiaṃ paṇamiūṇa su-guruṃ ca
								manda tti sasaraṇ-aṭṭhā Khittiviyārāṇum ucchāmi || 1 || </incipit>
							<explicit xml:lang="pra" type="mula"><locus from="42r" to="42r"
									>[42r1?]</locus> sesāṇa dīvāṇa taho dahīṇaṃ viyāra vitthāramaṇorapāraṃ,
								sayā suyāu paribhāvayantu savvapi savvattu mai kkavitta || 264 ||
								msūrīhiṃ jaṃ Rayaṇasehara-nāmaehi app'attham eva raiyam
								nara-khitta-vikkhaṃ saṃsohiyaṃ payaraṇaṃ suyaṇehi loe pāveu taṃ
								kusala-raṅga-maiṃ pasiddhiṃ || 265 || </explicit>
							<finalRubric xml:lang="pra" type="mula"><locus from="42r" to="42r"
									>[42r]</locus> iti śrīKhetasamāsa-sāvacūriḥ || cha || </finalRubric>
							<!--<colophon xml:lang="pra" type="mula"><locus from="20v" to="20v">[20v1]</locus>
</colophon>-->
							<note>Commentary</note>
							<!--<rubric xml:lang="gu" type="commentary"><locus from="1v" to="1v">[1v1]</locus> 
</rubric>-->
							<incipit xml:lang="gu" type="commentary"><locus from="1v" to="1v"
									>[1v1]</locus> śrīMahāvīra deva te kehavā chai jagaddiśva(ra) tihā
								śekhara-mukuṭa praṇamīnaiṃ āpaṇuṃ gurupaṇa mūrkha chau āpaṇa pānai
								samariyā Kṣetra-vicāranu ........tirichau eka rāja-kṣetra nai viṣai
								asaṅkhyātī dvīpa sahui te saghalā uddhāra palyopamanā pacavĪsa koḍākoḍī
								nā samayamāna dvīpa samudra jāṇi Kuru-kṣetra nā </incipit>
							<explicit xml:lang="gu" type="commentary"><locus from="42r" to="42r"
									>[42r?]</locus> tathā samudranau vicāra teha cha nu vistāra anant pāra
								nirantara śrute siddhānta thakī paribhākhyau saṃpūrṇa sarva janā-mataṃ
								naiṃ viṣai eka citra thakā || 264 || ācārya śrīRatnaśekhara nāmai
								stokārthā ji racitaṃ manuṣya-kṣetra nau vakhāṇa samyag prakāri sodhi kāu
								eka prakaraṇa sva-jana-loka pāmyauṃ te māṅgalikya raṅgamaya prasiddha
								samṛddhi || 265 || </explicit>
							<finalRubric xml:lang="sa" type="commentary"><locus from="42r" to="42r"
									>[42r?]</locus> iti śrīKṣetrasamāsa sūtra sācacūri samāptaṃ || 108(?)
								|| </finalRubric>
